constraints[0].fields[0]: a list index in a field must be a whole number, like input.listeners[0]
constraints[1].fields[0]: splat [*] must be followed by a field, like input.replicas[*].host
constraints[2].fields[0]: only one [*] is allowed in a field
constraints[3].fields[0]: a list index in a field must be a whole number, like input.listeners[0]
constraints[4].fields[0]: must be a input reference: write input.vpc-id
constraints[5].fields[0]: must be a input reference: write input.code.inline
